trans-unit.source: Ensures that an authentication object is present in the context.
trans-unit.target: Sikrer at det finnes et objekt med godkjenning i konteksten.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The DefaultAuthenticationModule ensures that the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance is set to an <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object for each request.
trans-unit.target: DefaultAuthenticationModule sikrer at den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomsten er satt til en <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objekt for hver forespørsel.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: The DefaultAuthenticationModule examines the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property after the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event and before the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: DefaultAuthenticationModule undersøker den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>etter at den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>hendelsen og før den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest> </xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property is `null`, the DefaultAuthenticationModule sets the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property to a <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal> object that contains no user information.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen `null`, DefaultAuthenticationModule angir den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen til en <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal>objekt som inneholder ingen brukerinformasjon.</xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the authentication module sets the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A> property to 401, the DefaultAuthenticationModule will render an access-denied error page.
trans-unit.target: Hvis modulen godkjenning angir den <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A>-egenskapen til 401 gjengi DefaultAuthenticationModule tilgang-feilmeldingssiden.</xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If the value of the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A> property is set to a value greater than 200, the DefaultAuthenticationModule object will end the request.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for den <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A>er satt til en verdi større enn 200, DefaultAuthenticationModule objektet avsluttes forespørselen.</xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.StatusCode%2A>

trans-unit.source: In that case, only HTTP modules that subscribe to the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest> event are called prior to the completion of the current request.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet bare HTTP-moduler som abonnerer på den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest>hendelsen kalles før fullføring av gjeldende forespørsel.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.EndRequest>

trans-unit.source: The DefaultAuthenticationModule exposes an <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Authenticate> event.
trans-unit.target: DefaultAuthenticationModule viser en <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>hendelse.</xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>

trans-unit.source: You can use this event to provide a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object for the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke denne hendelsen til å angi en egendefinert <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objekt den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate> event is accessed by specifying an event named **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** in the application's Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>hendelsen brukes ved å angi en hendelse navnet **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** i programmets Global.asax filen.</xref:System.Web.Security.WindowsAuthenticationModule.Authenticate>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: This constructor is not intended to be called from application code.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren skal ikke kalles fra programmet kode.

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET calls this constructor to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> class.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET kaller denne konstruktøren for å opprette en forekomst av <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>klassen.</xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: After calling the constructor, it calls the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Init%2A> method to initialize the new <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> object.
trans-unit.target: Etter kall til konstruktøren, kaller den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Init%2A>metode for å initialisere den nye <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>objektet.</xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule.Init%2A>

trans-unit.source: Occurs after the request has been authenticated.
trans-unit.target: Forekommer når forespørselen er godkjent.

trans-unit.source: The Authenticate event is raised after the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: Godkjenn denne hendelsen oppstår når den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: It is used to ensure that the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance is populated with an <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object.
trans-unit.target: Det brukes til å sikre at den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomsten er fylt med en <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can access the Authenticate event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> class by specifying a subroutine named **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** in the application's Global.asax file.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til hendelsen Godkjenn for den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>klassen ved å angi en underrutine navnet **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** i programmets Global.asax filen.</xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: You can use the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs.Context%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs> object in the **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event to set the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance to a custom <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> object.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs.Context%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs>objekt i den **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** -hendelsen for å angi den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomsten til en egendefinert <xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Principal.IPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs> </xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationEventArgs.Context%2A>

trans-unit.source: If you do not specify a value for the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property, the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> sets the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance to a <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal> object that contains no user information.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke angir en verdi for den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>egenskapen den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>angir den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for den <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomst til en <xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal>objekt som inneholder ingen brukerinformasjon.</xref:System.Security.Principal.GenericPrincipal> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> </xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: The **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event is raised after the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event and before the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest> event.
trans-unit.target: Den **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** denne hendelsen oppstår når den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>hendelsen og før den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthorizeRequest> </xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: If you have an section that depends on the user name to deny or allow access to your application, modifying the <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A> property of the current <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> instance can affect the behavior of your application.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du har en inndeling som er avhengig av brukernavnet for å tillate tilgang til programmet eller, endring av <xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>for gjeldende <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>forekomsten kan påvirke virkemåten for programmet.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext> </xref:System.Web.HttpContext.User%2A>

trans-unit.source: Be sure that the user name you set during the **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** event is considered when you specify the section in your configuration.
trans-unit.target: Kontroller at brukernavnet du setter under den **DefaultAuthentication_OnAuthenticate** hendelsen anses når du angir delen i konfigurasjonen.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > If the Web application is running in IIS 7.0 in Integrated mode, the Authenticate event of the <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule> is not raised.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Hvis webprogrammet kjører i IIS 7.0 i integrert modus, hendelsen Godkjenn for den <xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>ikke starter.</xref:System.Web.Security.DefaultAuthenticationModule>

trans-unit.source: If the `mode` attribute of the configuration element is set to "None" and the application subscribes to the Authenticate event, a <xref:System.PlatformNotSupportedException> error is raised.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den `mode` attributtet for konfigurasjonselementet er satt til "None", og programmet abonnerer på hendelsen Godkjenn en <xref:System.PlatformNotSupportedException>feil oppstår.</xref:System.PlatformNotSupportedException>

trans-unit.source: In this scenario, to receive authentication notification, subscribe to the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest> event of the <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> instance.
trans-unit.target: I dette tilfellet for å motta varsel authentication abonnere på den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>hendelsen til den <xref:System.Web.HttpApplication>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.HttpApplication> </xref:System.Web.HttpApplication.AuthenticateRequest>

trans-unit.source: For more information about compatibility issues in Integrated mode, see [Moving an ASP.NET Application from IIS 6.0 to IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om kompatibilitetsproblemer i integrert modus, se [flytter en ASP.NET-programmet fra IIS 6.0 til IIS 7.0](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
